# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),

## Unreleased

### Added

 - Added work-item overrides
    ```json
    workItems {
        type "User Story" {
            state "Review Internally" color="#FFFFFF"
            state "Review with Customer" color="#FFFFFF"
        }
    }
    ```
 - fix: toc grid size overflow when work items have long titles

